    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept and attractive, this is a good honest example that presents nicely and is ready to be enjoyed right away. It shows well overall with the kind of light age and use you\u2019d expect from a driver-quality car, but it still has a clean, cared-for look that makes it easy to feel good about owning. A strong choice for someone who wants a nice car without paying mint-condition money.",
