    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Rough, incomplete driver/project car in poor overall condition. This is not a clean or sorted example, and buyers should expect significant cosmetic wear, an aged interior, and multiple needs before it could be considered dependable for regular use. Best suited for someone looking for a restoration project, a budget entry point, or a parts car, depending on their plans. It presents honestly as a tired vehicle that has seen heavy use and will require time, money, and mechanical attention.",
