    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition car that presents nicely and appears complete, usable, and ready to enjoy as a solid driver. Paint, trim, and interior show normal age and use, with some minor cosmetic flaws and wear you\u2019d expect from an older vehicle, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. It should make a satisfying driver for someone who wants a car they can use and enjoy right away, while still understanding it is not a freshly restored or perfect example.",
