    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Practical, affordable, and priced to move, this vehicle is a great fit for a buyer seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values function and value over cosmetics, but it still offers a lot of utility for the money. An honest, budget-conscious option with plenty of potential for the right owner.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with a lot of life experience and plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great option for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone needing basic transportation without spending a fortune. It starts, runs, and offers a practical foundation for a fixer-upper, daily runabout, or project. If you appreciate honest value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with strong mechanical character. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers dependable run-and-drive capability and a willing powertrain that pulls cleanly. A good candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation, a shop truck, or a platform to sort and improve over time. Straightforward, honest, and priced for someone who understands value in a usable driver rather than a showroom piece.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Honest poor-condition car with solid value for the money. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with grit, character, and a story already written into every mile. This is the kind of ride that speaks to someone who sees possibility where others only see age\u2014a dependable companion for the hands-on driver, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for affordable wheels with personality. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh; instead, it offers honest, lived-in charm and the chance to make it your own. If you want a budget-friendly vehicle with heart and plenty of potential, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
